JOHN H. PULESTON et at., Plaintiffs and Appellants, v. FRANCIS B. WALLACE, et al., Defendants and Respondents. Appeal from a judgment entered upon the report of a referee in favor of defendants, dismissing the complaint.

Before Monell and Van Vorst, JJ.

Decided February 1, 1873. W. F. Church, for appellants. William Fullerton, for respondents. Judgment affirmed.

No opinion rendered.
